video_title: Keep your eyes ON THE GOAL  #motivation #adviceoftheday #podcast #mindsetpodcast
transcript:
when you focus on what you don't want
you tend to end up getting what you
don't want don't look at the crash
because you will go where you're looking
he goes you have to look past the crash
or else you will hit your friend and
that clicked in my head cuz I was like
man that is life like how often do we
look at the crash the that could be our
life in the future and we're like I
don't want this I don't I just don't
want to be broke anymore I just don't
want to have bad relationships I don't I
don't I don't and we're focusing we
putting energy into what we don't want
versus putting energy into what we do
want
